  "keyFeatures": [
    "End-to-end multimodal document processing pipeline (PDF, Office, images, text)",
    "Specialized modal processors for images, tables, mathematical equations, and custom types",
    "Multimodal knowledge graph with cross-modal entity extraction and relationship discovery",
    "Multiple parser backends: MinerU, Docling, PaddleOCR",
    "Three query modes: pure text, VLM-enhanced, and multimodal queries",
    "Direct content list insertion for pre-parsed or programmatically generated content",
    "Batch processing with parallel workers and progress tracking",
    "Context-aware multimodal analysis using surrounding document content",
    "Built on LightRAG for hybrid vector-graph retrieval"
